Stavařky and an interior design and have the possibility to combine a job with the care of the child.
Miniškolku devised their own staff arch. design, and with the support of the leadership they managed to get the grant of the European Union and the Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs.
Corporate miniškolka is financed from the resources of the European Social Fund, through the operational programme human resources and employment and the state budget of the Czech Republic.
