The house of bones fascinates even after 100 years. look into the interior from Gaudí
The roof looks like the back of ancient lizard, staircases reminds the backbone of Dinosaur and balconies are open to fish mouth.
This is the house of the Casa Batlló in Barcelona from the catalonian Antoni Gaudí architect.
From the local house, thanks to its organic shapes called the house of bones.
Organic forms, wild colors, an unusual use of stone, fragments of kachlů and mosaic, facade of scales and pervasive soft curves, all this is typical for secession Antoni Gaudí.
The front of the house making a dreamlike line, gentle colors and textures reminiscent of the nature and animals.
As you can see geometričnost, rhythm and exactly a coherent procedure.
On the night of the facade home sounds more dramatically, is nasvícená so that the impression of color still potentiated by.
Winding up and twisting shapes in the same way also appear in the interiors.
The wood in waves copying the window frames, rail, decorative elements of the door, the Watch and bar.
The house Batlló, which is in the area of Eixample to purchase a busy street Passeig de Grácia No 43, a conversion house from 1877 from the architect Emilio Sala Cortese.
The reconstruction of the two years, and the house was completed in 1906.
The investor, rich industrialist Josep Batlló, originally insisted on old buildings and the construction of a completely new, but it soon Gaudí accepted the idea of the unusual and cheaper reconstruction.
Apartment house Casa Batlló but Antoni Gaudí design it alone.
He cooperated with him architect Josep Maria Jujol.
It is on his projektantském plank arose decoration for Retail apartment owners of the real estate, use of mosaic on the facade.
The facade worked as a number of other writers and artists.
The common work on the proposals of the house Casa Batlló was triggered by the successful cooperation with Jujola Gaudím.
Jujol participated in the construction of the house Gaudí Casa nice and park Güell, in which they are more Gaudí works.
From the local house, soon after the completion of earned by its organic shapes the nickname `` house of bones. "
Others are due to the specific mechanism of opening the windows came to call `` zívajícím house. "
It is also said that at the top of the building 's vypodobněn sword St George, patron of Catalonia.
The hidden motives contain religious and other sculptural elements of the building.
Gaudí into the house suggested the unique system of central heating with odvětrávacími vents and typical of chimneys.
The bizarre may seem their forty - five - degree slope.
In the formation of the Gaudí absolutely not respect the building codes and leave them tie.
At the beginning of the construction has received from the town of a building permit, but it referred to the data on the planned reconstruction were vague enough that two years later in the completion of the City Council was the result of horrified and sought to remedy.
Councillor mind, for example, that construction intervened pillars and into the public the sidewalk.
To remedy never took place, on the contrary: only fifteen days after the invitation parts of the city 's Josep Batlló applied for (and successfully) received permission to hire two highest floors of the building.
The owner himself into lower levels.
In the gallery on the second floor was the and on the third floor bedroom and private parts of the apartment.
The ground floor was rented jewelry.
The whole house šestipatrový intersects the staircase, which could be climbed up on the roof terrace.
The essential elements of perestroika was lifting all right angles and direct lines and their replacement curved walls.
Gaudí also worked with the concept of a modern interconnection of space.
Social part of the opening of the door orchestr can be quite link and greater, the company can easily communicate, while at the same time, to the privacy of the necessary for a more intimate talks.
The house with Gaudí conversion, in addition to the new facade of a non - traditional roofs and two floors.
Impressive is also Gaudí game with the light, blue and white glazed tiles, which is in the inner court, and skylights.
The game two colors, he adds a maximum of light in all floors of the house.
It was simply bet on the principle that white reflects the light of more than a dark, which the sun 's rays, on the other hand, absorbing.
The house of the Casa Batlló, who was in 2005 included in the UNESCO World Heritage, may each visit.
On the first floor of the house is the largest and grandest apartment made available to the public.
The owners are for this step decided to in 2002, on the occasion of the celebration of a hundred the fiftieth anniversary of the birth of the famous artist.
In the case of the inspections remained, because they found that it is a very good company, and the spread of common and attic rooms, including the roof terrace.
Admission to the memory of it certainly is not negligible, 16,50 EUR, students, pensioners, the group and holders of tourist průkazek have a 20% discount.
The sum of more than the price of admission to other Gaudí buildings in the town.
If you want to taste the right of the house with the dragon steeples, you must be quick to make friends with one of the population of the building and to visit him directly at home.
How to choose the mattress and grid: women have requirements other than men
Rather than its tupolevs the bed frame, but the quality of lehací area, i. e., the mattress and grid, give the basis for a really good bed.
They must, however, be harmoniously complement to meet the specific user.
In the selection of the casting lots of things, from a height, weight, age, health, and gender owner.
An important is also the type of the interior, in which the mattress and grate buying.
A typical example?
The need for weekend cottage where regularly heated, are not suitable latex mattresses, because they are more slowly, `` warmed ."
Moreover, they tend to have a significantly higher than the standard PUR mattresses.
It is necessary to be regularly.
If they do not have a lot of the dump channels, in the core, and is still lies on the board, holds humidity: could be under them appear even mold.
In the selection shall also habit.
Who spent time abroad, where are often used a lot of high mattresses are změkčující layer, it 's hard to feel good at low and with a hard surface.
`` All the players who were returning from the NHL, to me, that 's sleep. "
