The pressure is located in a more points and reduces tension.
Of course, as soon as you use on the mattress and grate bad pillow (big and `` plump "), most of the `` plus" disappears.
The basic rule is simple: the pillow to buttress his head and not only to my shoulders, in order to release the shoulder muscles.
As the appropriate size is recommended 50 x 60 cm, which they prefer to, for example, in Scandinavia.
