The instruments for the monitoring of people want to increasingly parents, so they want to prepare for their children
Fear for their own child brings more and more people to the idea of watching over the GPS.
The system was originally created for the search for cars may have to follow the movement of people, and the aid should in such cases, which is the disappearance of the nine - year - old Annie Janatkové.
The device is not about the size of a box of matches, but soon, it may be the only as a watch.
A number of people scared case vanished Annie and began to the quest for resources, as their children better protect.
Even at the price of their privacy.
`` We are all say that it is not about spying, but on the next to reduce the likelihood that 's a tragedy, "says Petr sawdust of society, Macro Weil, which is one of the suppliers of surveillance equipment on the czech market.
`` I admit that in any case, may result in abuse of such equipment, even if you are in the bag of someone who does not know about it, but we have not met with such a case. "
`` Most of it actually customers are buying for security reasons, "he added sawdust.
According to him, would always child should know to what purpose is `` the box "is used, and how to use in an emergency.
Child psychologist Dana Bočková points out that, if the child will not want anything like to wear, just to get rid of it.
`` Even very small children show great creativity in how some things on purpose to lose, when they do not want to be under control. "
`` Great expectations raised previously in my parents' cell phones, but which can turn off as well as the tracking device, "says Bočková.
In accordance with it is doubtful that in the case of the attack, indeed, such a device would help.
`` As regards the forthcoming kidnapping, it will ensure the perpetrator virtually always it that the child had no electronics, which would give away his position. "
`` It is now the phone. "
`` When you start to expand the tracking device will also find them, because of their sales must be supported by a massive advertisement. "
`` In this case, the criminals always one step ahead of the police, "says psychologist.
He added, however, that a similar device may help in the case of a sudden assault.
By Robert czechs from the company RC monitoring, which offers a surveillance services for both cars, so for persons, even in the event occurs after the attack immediately to the destruction of the surveillance equipment, may his presence of assistance.
`` The device can be set on regular sending position after a certain period of time. "
`` If the damage was done, will be available for at least the last position of the person concerned. "
