The U. S. Army put in Afghanistan, a new `` smart "weapon, known as yet only under the code mark XM - 25.
The generals, hope that the new automatic rifle will affect the conflict with the Taliban and `` change the game "in their favor.
A new weapon is something like a small superpřesné happening.
Her projectiles, taking the laser to within a few meters.
Special calibre bullets 25 mm, developed for this rifle and containing a highly explosive charge, in fact, acting as a small grenades.
The bullets can be programmed so that they are not only an impact on the objectives, but at any point in their ballistic runway.
Therefore can be used against the enemy, which lies behind some obstacle, behind the wall or in the trenches.
From above, usually is not protected, and when he can bear the murderous rain steel fragments, it may override it from a fight.
