Do not forget, during his training on the southern and patriotic put the icing on the cake: `` the italian Gelato is simply the best - and then it was still notná dose of romance. "
The first step of the manufacturing appears to be relatively simple.
Luciano inserts basic ingredients milk, cream, milk powder, sugar and stabilisers into a great mixer, which all by electronic program to 85 degrees and subsequently now cool to four degrees.
Then he turns to tap and comes a pasterizovaný white basic cream, the basis of all kinds of milk - based ice - cream.
Now it is Associate Professor caved in issues: it is possible to make an ice cream only from natural substances, without stabilizer?
How can a man alone experiment?
Luciano warns, to be carried away by the spirit of the times into the unknown.
Who speaks about ice cream `` only from natural ingredients ," as used stabilizers - usually a natural product, as is Guar flour from guar grains.
Of course, it is possible to make an ice cream, even without stabilizers, but to sell in one day, or you will drive down and the customer her all grains of ice.
A variation of the matter is permissible.
More excitin 's will be with flavouring essences.
Maestro Luciano distinguishes the taste of ice cream, according to the ingredients to buy in a supermarket either in the department with fruit or in the Department of sweets.
In addition, there are pills and creams.
`` Suppliers trying to impose a lot of aromatized ingredients. "
`` You should be but simply experiment. "
Either with fruit sorbets with sugar and fresh fruit.
Or with ice cream of white fundamental matter, amend the eggs at the yellow cream and cocoa on the basis for some chocolate temptation.
Now, may be involved in the course of an ice cream machines.
Do it to make every four different kinds of vanilla, chocolate, coffee and lískooříškové ice - cream - either with eggs or without them in the mass, with more or less vanilla flavouring or other natural ingredients.
The same experiment shall also be carried out with fruit types of ice cream.
More aromatic substances, more fruit purée - due to taste it is always better.
Lískooříšková ice cream may enjoy more butter pecan, if it contains more hazelnut.
Most popular kiwi ice cream constructed group, which use more fruit, less water and a little less stabilizer.
Only when the balanced combination of highlighting the right to Gelato, says Luciano.
The production of ice - cream is purely numerous task: when using a peach purée with a lot of sugar, it must be to reduce the share of sugar in the basic recipe.
In the case of lemon ice - cream is the need for an extra ration of sugar.
He takes Luciano machine, which specifies the sugar content in fruit (vintners the measured the must from grapes).
Fortunately, reduce the number of the table.
The production of ice - cream does not require much physical exertion as before.
Do not only instrument for the automatic production of the matter.
