This claim could make the judge to address the question of whether with the emergence of new technologies that also new rules in the courtroom.
`` As i have seen in this trial, i think that there is a real danger that the inclusion of new technologies in the courtroom affects the rights of due process for individuals, "said Thomas J. Ullmann, the attorney, Mr. Reuben Hayes.
