Zapatero and red line of german
BERLIN decided to maintain the euro, but set down the conditions for the whole Union.
The tension in the markets of a double the government 's response.
On the one hand he suggested José Luis Zapatero new adaptation measures, from the tax cuts for small and medium - sized enterprises, through the regulation of private agencies or repeal the 426 euro for the unemployed without benefits, after privatisation 49% (AENA spanish airports and air traffic management, manager of airports Barajas and El Prat and 30% of the state lottery.
Vice - president Elena Salgadová with the support of the former Prime Minister Felipe is, on the other hand, joined the critiques of to address Chancellor Angela Merkel because of its responsibility for the launch of the current crisis.
How to interpret this emotion?
So be it in advance that the opinion of Merkel 's mistake in its communication policy.
On the contrary, it is another point in a complex process redefinitions of the euro.
And here, Germany has a radically new vision of what is to be his future, which is referring to the idea of compliance with the old traditions, which holds a large part of the other members.
In the face of the European resistance in Germany is beginning to speculate about three ways of the crisis.
The first one is the strong euro zone, which would be, Germany, but also, for example, Austria, and the Netherlands, while the southern states would have left the currency zone.
The second is a return to the mark - though now it may seem like a science - fiction, this version has a broad public support, close to 50% of the population.
The third option is, according to the german proposals for a revision of the euro, with more macroeconomic supervision, budgetary rigor of, penalties for the offending states, possible delays payment for some of them, and with the enlargement of the possible costs on the regulation on the private sector.
Germany 's position is clear and already had some time defines, so there is no room for evasion by now.
First, when in 2009, the International Monetary Fund, and the European Commission to encourage deficits, pulled from the german government constitutional reform, in order to prevent them from 2016.
This was the first sign of conflict between what Germany regarded as the right (plans fiscal stringency of, and the stability of public finances), and what they were practicing its european partners, including France.
The second showed this central european countries, if Merkel painfully stretched out of the decision on the rescue of Greece.
It was the subject of a serious criticism, but the truth is that the political consensus in Germany and public opinion, which was also published were heavily against the rescue of Greece.
Finally, in the last October 's days, Merkel again with a clear opinion, when requested to reform the Convention, the European Union so as to allow for the rescue of a Member State, and at the same time, to have a private creditors to bear part of the costs.
This opinion was interpreted as anti - european, as accelerated the irish crisis, and everything else.
But its proposal, although in a slightly as mitigated by the form, was approved, and over the next few months, we should follow the reform process of the Union, which should from 2013 to enable these measures.
Germany by the red line, which will not exceed.
And all tells us that, although there is now a need to do the measures, which probably too does not agree, from that date will be with an old functioning of the end of the euro.
Year 2013 will represent the birth of a new currency zone in which nations will offending hard sanctioned and may be forced to announce the postponement of payments, and the private sector will also need to bear part of the costs.
Germany us suggests that we have to give a strict way the growth is increasing the savings and investment, moderate consumption, improvements in productivity and competitiveness, and capital reserves.
Another option based on claims and building, with huge gaps in the balance of payments, was in the years boom of the growth of Spain, simply are not going to tolerate.
The offer is clear.
And we will make a mistake, if they fail to understand.
It is not only on the renewal of the public deficits at 3% in 2013.
What they want us to do, it is much harder.
And the worst thing is that under these conditions could happen to us, they were wrong.
I hope that the current turbulence will replace more quiet.
And to take advantage of the opportunity that gives us in the spring of 2013.
It seems that the Prime Minister Zapatero, it also understood and his dual Declaration promised reform after meeting with large companies from last Saturday and yesterday 's notification of new measures) suggests that, in spite of criticism of Merkel has opened the way to the idea that there is a need to put things right.
But the red line, which Germany set, it is here, and it does not seem to be with her to move.
And of the options, over which can be considered can not abandon the euro - zone of a serious countries ruled out.
Well, Germany will always be able to say that the us warned.
Sport and circumvent the rules
Tricks, what do Alonso and Ramos in a struggle with Ajaxem, show the wit not intention to escape punishment.
Supposedly zosnovaná exclusion of two players currency Madrid (Xabiho Alonsa and Sergio Ramos) in the struggle against the Champions League Ajax of 23 November meant that was launched a sea of ink about whether this is or is not unsportsmanlike and whether or not the state - of - the - both footballers punish.
As is well known, a few minutes before the end of the game (who had their team clearly vou take), appointed by the players, one after the other deliberately losing time at the moment when he had a foul play, so as to provoke the judge, and he showed them a second yellow card.
In this way, the two contestants fulfill the punishment in the struggle against the Real Madrid Auxerre - end in his group in the lead - and will be able to, deprived of the cards, continue on to the next phase.
Finally, the Disciplinary Board UEFA coach José Mourinhovi punishment for two games and leading players got a financial penalty.
The provocation yellow cards in similar circumstances, is not a new practice, but it is more or less in football, the normal.
It is so widespread, that is part of the ethos of football, so the rules, which are not unwritten, but they are.
Part of the discussion in this case was due to the fact that it was a member of the team Real Madrid (which, in their national anthem boasts magnanimity and honor, and which has a similar actions of his players pokutoval), and as it seems, thanks to the drama, led by the Mourinhem, which was added to its long history actor and provocateur another episode.
In any case, the debate about whether this kind of negotiations, which is not the rules expressly prohibited, is contrary to the principles of the sport, i. e., whether in these deeds circumvention of the law; it is indeed the actions of respecting sporting rules, whose sense, however, it seems, is trying to bypass.
Dealing with the type of damage such negotiations is a spirit of sport.
One of the requirements of sportsmanship is the physical integrity opponents, who was not in these cases violated, or to avoid violent game.
Another one of these formalities characterise the net game is to ensure that the players because of his transgression had vis - à - vis the team opponent advantage - which also here.
Thus, the paradox of action players currency Madrid is the fact that he had not, as normally charakterizujeme as a ruse or circumvention of the law, not to a breach of the rules in order to avoid the penalty, but this behavior should be seen as much as possible in order to obtain a penalty.
Wait and like punishment.
Another question, however, is that the advantage of the guilty from his deliberate infringement will have.
Here, it is to be noted that the opponent getting into the handicaps, and that in the current struggle can not get any benefit, as an obvious result is that team itself will have less players.
And it 's not even a useful strategy to another struggle, since the club will not be able to these players count.
Obviously, the advantage lies in the fact that the players to the next stage of the Champions League without the cards, which might endanger their participation in the future.
However, this is an advantage of the long - term perspective, and with a certain degree of uncertainty, i. e., at first sight, the team may be eliminated, and outside the following negotiations will have players punishment, and go to the second round of cards, in which the exclusion of just about one card less than in the first round.
So what will be the wheels continue, it is not clear whether it is the advantage.
And, in short, these negotiations are against the spirit of sport, which is to make the strategic decisions, which will make it possible to obtain the maximum benefit within the rules.
In the event that we should not players to avoid the penalty (which would be a clear case of circumvention of the rules), but rather have chosen to obey him.
Did the strategic decision without, avoiding the punishment or fled before him.
Although it is not the borders between the wit and circumvention clear, i believe that, in this case is clearly a wit.
It seems to me that the controversy exists for two reasons: because it was about two samovyloučení and because of the way in which the transfer of instructions to their provoking from the management.
The damage to the sports principles of these actions is not so ethical as aesthetic.
