South Korea 's government adopted by the law, called the `` peciválský, "which will prohibit adolescentům play on - line game after midnight, that block access to them, they said responsible government officials.
The bill will be submitted to Parliament in December, so that he could ask companies operating on - line game of blocking access to these games after midnight to anyone under 16 years, the leaders of the Ministry of Culture and the Ministry for the family.
`` Many children playing these games all night and then have problems with learning in school, and they are not able to lead a normal life during the day. "
`` We believe that the law is necessary for it, to ensure their health and their right to sleep, "said for AFP yeah Rin, the leading factor in the Ministry of, which has a bill to worry about.
On - line game will be newly accessible from 6 in the morning.
The company will have one year to prepare for the application of the law, clarified.
The government also assumes that, at the request of the company to limit the day - to - day time access to these games for young, whose parents so requests, the said responsible official.
