Vindictive hackers and přičinliví spies
Case WikiLeaks has a double meaning.
On the one hand, it is exposed manifest scandal, scandal, which seems to be the only in the face of hypocrisy, which shall be governed by the relations between states, citizens and the press.
On the other hand, indicative of the deep changes at the international level, and anticipates future ruled by regression.
But let 's go over in order.
The first aspect of wikileaks, it is a fact that any document drawn up by the secret service (any nation) consists exclusively of printing cuts.
`` Extraordinary discovery "Americans about the way of life sexually Berlusconi 's reported that what you are already for months, everyone can read in any (all except those two Berlusconi' s own), and a profile of karikaturní Kadáfího was for a long time for neuro artist topic for the sketches..
The rule that classified documents may consist only of the reports of the already known, it is essential in the dynamics of the intelligence services, and not only in this century.
If you are going to the bookstore, dedicated to ezoterické literature, you will see that each of repeated (about Graalu, mystery rennes - le - Château, templářích or freemasons, if i might) exactly what it has been written previously.
And it is not only that the author of the occult texts i searching for new information (even knows where to find the reports of the non - existent), but because those who are engaged in the occult believe only what we know and what it confirms what had already learned.
It is a mechanism for the success of Dan Brown.
The same applies to the secret papers.
The informant 's lazy, and lazy (or a limited spirit), head of the secret service (and, if not, it could be, as i know, editor in the papers Libération), which it considers true only what he himself admits.
Information with high suppression of Berlusconi, which the US embassy sent to the government, the same which Newsweek published a week before.
Why, then, around the discovery of these documents do so much?
On the one hand, they say what every cultured man he knows, and that was the embassy, at least since the end of World War II, and since you may heads of state to call or fly the plane on common dinner, lost its diplomatic function and, with the exception of a few small exercise in representation be transformed in Intelligence.
Any spectator watching films on investigations very well it knows that only from self - righteousness, it seemed to ignore.
Nevertheless, the fact that it was repeated publicly, decries the obligation of hypocrisy and hurled it bad light on american diplomacy.
Second, the idea that any hacker may obtain the strictest classified information, the most powerful country in the world is a hard blow, rather than a substantial, for the prestige of the national government.
The scandal affects how victims, as well as his `` U ."
But let 's get out of here to the truth about what happened.
Once, in times of Orwell, it was possible to absorb all too, like some kind of Big Brother, who has checked every movement of its people.
Orvellovo prophecy was demonstrated, since by the ability to control every move, thanks to the phone, each of the transaction, visited Hotel, used the highway, and so on, became a citizen of the victims of power.
But, as demonstrated how it is now, that even a `` tomb "with nejtajnějšími information powerful can not resist intervention a hacker, ceases to be the control report a one - way and becomes a circular.
The power controls every citizen, but every citizen, or at least a hacker - the chosen as a citizen of the Avenger - may know all the secrets of power.
How can he hold power, which has no chance to keep their own secret?
It is true that the already Georg Simmel said that the true secret is bezobsažné secret (and bezobsažné secrets it could never be revealed); it is also true that all the information about the nature of Berlusconi 's or Merkel is really mysterious bezobsažným secret, because it is drawn from public life; but to detect, just as it did WikiLeaks, that the mystery Hillary Clinton was bezobsažnými secrets, means withdraw him all power.
WikiLeaks did not do any mistake in Sarkozy 's or Merkel, but it did something big Clinton and Obama.
What will be the consequences of this blow bestowed upon the powers so significant?
It is clear that, in the future, states will not be able to send the on - line of sensitive information - it would be tantamount to its disclosure on a poster taped on the corner of the street.
But it is also clear that the current technology is unnecessary hope that can be sustained in undercover reports on the phone.
Nothing is easier than to determine if and when the head of state travelling by air and joined with some of his colleagues.
How can be maintained in the classification of private and sensitive news?
Well, i know that, for the moment has forecast belongs to the science - fiction, and it is therefore a fantastic, but i have to imagine the government officials, who shall be transported discreetly carrying out formalities after uncontrollable routes and carrying around only those reports that they know from memory, or rather hiding rare information in his shoes.
Information is retained in a unique copies in drawers concluded the key: the whole, an attempt to espionage in the case of the Watergate had a little success than WikiLeaks.
I have had the opportunity to write that the technology is now moving sideways ahead, it means backwards.
A century after the wireless telegraph revolutionized the roads, Internet rehabilitating telegraph, based on the wires (telephone).
Video (analogue) to allow for lovers of a movie film scanning step by step, push it back and forth and reveal all the secrets of the assembly, while now CD (digital) allow only jumping on chapters, that is, after makroporcích.
Through the high - speed train will arrive from Rome to Milan in three hours, while on the air travel and transport, which includes the need for three and a half hours.
It is thus exceptional that politics and communications technology will return to the wagons towed horses.
The last note.
At other times, the press tried to understand what had in secret embassy.
Now they are embassy, which are confidential information from the press.
The climate is: how France hackla their promises of financing
A year after the Copenhagen agreement, it is time to check compliance with promises to quickly odblokovaná financing (which financing with Quick Start (fast start) or premature), followed by the developed countries.
And the French hacky were disclosed
In the Copenhagen Agreement developed countries committed to provide 30 billion in 2010 - 2012.
The European Union has promised 7,2 billion for three years, and France, 26 1 billion (that is, 420 million per year).
At the start of the COP 16 pulled out of the EU 's big ace, to convince its partners of the reality of its commitment to the financing of fast start: report detailing the action of its Member States, press conference, Grand side - by - side refrigerators event, distribute pamphlets...
Transparent operation invaluable and priced at their real value: the advanced countries and civil society, that 's all the advanced countries and civil society amounted to the same, and with the same degree of precision.
The EU announces that in 2010 €2,2 billion, making it brings on the right path to comply with its promise of 7,2 billion in 2012.
But if we focus on detail, we will find that things are much more complicated.
These funds are under the Copenhagen agreement `` new and additional "to ensure that is increased burden implemented, without having to the detriment of public support for the development.
Unfortunately, there is no consensus on what it means `` a new and additional ."
While the European Commission has proposed harmonisation, some Member States, among others, and France, the process of blocked.
Today, each picks the reference, which fits him best.
The European Commission, for example, considered the reference year 2009: the international finance, too, and she still adds 150 million to three years of financing fast start.
Other countries have chosen a similar References with annual payment deadlines or with terms at the level of public support for the development.
By contrast, France considers that the financing of `` all new projects "by 2010 are `` new and additional."
In other words, there is no reference to the expenditure for the previous period, or to the global level of public support for the development of the d 'Aide publique au développement.
Specifically, the total amount of aid, France to countries in the developing may remain unchanged (or even decrease), has complied with its obligation relating to the financing of the `` new and additional ."
Next, a crucial element is the division of the grants and loans.
There, there is no rule and everyone will choose their own method of calculation.
Some, like France, consider that, 1 €loaned amount to €1 minute.
Obviously, it 's hard to demonstrable: the effort is not equivalent.
If the application of loans can be demonstrated for certain investments, which are profitable (often on projects related to reducing emissions, consisting of more efficient technologies), it is foolish to present one euro, which will, as the equivalent of one of the euro, which we..., we should not be seen by virtue of their obligations, but as the cost of borrowing for the creditor country (i. e. the equivalent of interest rates).
But France may submit only such reasons: `` the "its commitment of 420 million, makes that 91,5% of the loan (389,8 million) and 8 5% of the gifts (36,1 million) - see the EU to allow themselves to verify.
It is the only country of the Union, which on such a scale uses a loan.
Germany was required 46%, while the Denmark, the Netherlands, or Slovakia (among others) comply with their obligations to 100% of the gifts.
In other words, if the vast majority of the European Union to €1 to the satisfaction of his promise, France can only 10 centimes and considers this effort for a comparable.
A beautiful kejklířský piece!
In summary, in its financing of `` fast start "France is operating with dual šejdířstvím: on the one hand, with the development of the shares in time, and on the other side with the real financial burden.
Although spends only 36,1 million, can be convinced that the issue of 420 million `` new and additional "in connection with their promises.
The manipulation of Finance Minister (because it seems that, although it 's Bercy, who was such a decision) would have the double negative impact, at the same time, within the EU (why the Member States continue donation, if only to borrow?) and in negotiations, because the developing countries are not entirely.
CHAPTER early financing is only a small otázečkou, a relatively short - term, in relation to a series of discussions on climate.
But it could be a grain of sand, moreover, in the enormous machine, which is the UNFCCC.
Let us hope that this is not the case.
Whether anything, it is necessary to draw the knowledge of this first year of the early financing.
Soon should France to announce a change in my way of accounting for the years 2011 and 2012, in compliance with their obligations and decency and justice to the other countries of the European Union.
But, above all, France should avoid debate on deposits in the long - term financing (other crucial chapter currently under consideration): will the issue of `` the additionality "or on the posting loans.
France should change its position in order to become so pokrokářská for these deposits, as it is for the other.
All hope is inserted into the new Minister for the Environment, Mrs Kosciusko - Morizetové, which is coming to Cancun next week.
Surprising announcement of fast launch of France and its vision of `` the additionality "and the use of loans could give rise to an increase in the level of international confidence, to the necessary in order to be able to go in discussions.
The alarm pesticides, which children engulfed.
Ten - year - old child will devour one day 81 various chemicals, according to a study published this center, from the Association of future generations (ex - movement, and the maintenance of future generations).
The association, which points out that the results of the `` do not have a significant statistical value with regard to the low number of samples analysed, but are characteristic of the pending issues, "i bought between July and September food commonly consumed by in four meals and a slight food as a light lunch for one child roughly ten - year in supermarkets in L 'of Oise and in Paris.
The typical food, including the official recommendations - five pieces of fresh fruit and vegetables, three milk products and 1,5 litres of water a day - as well as confectionery, were analysed research laboratories to chemicals, pesticides, heavy metals and other contaminating agents.
The balance of the plates is overwhelming: 81 chemicals, 42 ranks among the carcinogenic, possible or likely, and five substances are among the clear carcinogenic substances, as much as 37 substances, which could act as a troublesome for glands with the internal secretions (PE), according to the studies several institutions, such as the International Centre for cancer research.
`` Even if in almost all cases, legal limits for each chemical adopted individually are not exceeded, in our research okay, we see that reality in consumer exposure kontaminujícím carcinogenic substances, perhaps, and / or PE is astonishing, "the association.
For breakfast butter and tea with milk containing themselves about ten résiduí to possible carcinogenic effects and three identified as a carcinogen, as in the case of about twenty residues, which could distort hormonal system.
An apple, imported from Brazil, studies referred to as a small snack, contains traces of six chemicals, inter alia, in France banned fungicidal resource.
The same applies to the Green beans from Kenyi, covered by lunchtime, for which the study found traces of strong insecticides banned within the EU.
Moreover, the steak from minced meat, tuna in a can, and even the bread and gum were punctuated with pesticides, and other chemicals.
In the water from the tap analysis has revealed the presence of nitrates and chloroform.
Salmon Steak for dinner was `` the richest "with 34 objevenými chemical reziduy and even analysis of plastic plates used for heating food in the microwave to be analysis.
The final risk for the consumer of this `` Cocktail contaminants "is likely to be underestimated," resulting from the study.
The ecological Europe - green (EE, LV) proposed `` in the face of an emergency situation "to establish a moratorium on the use of pesticides to stop, `` the increase of civilization diseases."
In July, the study of the European Food Safety Agency (EFSA) examined the status of the presence of residues 365 different pesticide identified in the fruit and vegetables consumed in Europe, of the 76 in cereáliích.
